name: Re:Discover - A Wandering Mind Project
description:
Re:Discover is an auditory experience where you can navigate in a virtual world to generate a soundscape. There is a local coherence between the sounds, creating thematic zones recognizable by the human being.
To navigate, either control the position directly with the side panel or use ZQSD/WASD, depending on your keyboard language. Active the "online audio" option to hear the audio near you and "show points" to see them.
